      "name": "ASTM F1717 compression-bending operating envelope for non-cannulated 7.5 mm construct",
      "description": "Valid operating range: axial compressive preload 0–100 N; bending moment applied via 40 mm offset at crosshead displacement rates 1–5 mm/min; test temperature 22 ± 3 °C; UHMWPE vertebral body block hardness 55–65 Shore D; screw insertion torque 4.0–6.0 N·m; rod diameter 5.5 mm CoCr; construct span L4–L5 equivalent (40 mm pedicle-to-pedicle). Predictions outside these bounds require re-evaluation of model applicability."
    }
